          <ul class="clarity-who__list clarity-who__list--for">
            <li><span class="clarity-who__arrow">→</span> People who take their health seriously and want a physician program structured around prevention — more signal, real follow-through, a doctor who stays with you</li>
            <li><span class="clarity-who__arrow">→</span> Anyone who's done a one-time physical or ordered their own labs and found the data valuable but disconnected from an ongoing care relationship</li>
            <li><span class="clarity-who__arrow">→</span> Those who already track sleep, nutrition, or fitness with wearables and want a physician who can read that data in full clinical context</li>
