        <h2 class="clarity-h2">What this replaces. And what it costs.</h2>
        <p class="clarity-pricing__intro">The Clarity Program sits between fragmented self-directed testing and the ultra-premium longevity clinics — delivering clinical rigor and a physician relationship at a price that reflects the Main Line, not Manhattan or Scottsdale.</p>

        <div class="clarity-pricing__compare">
          <div class="clarity-compare-card">
            <h3 class="clarity-h3">vs. Executive physicals</h3>
            <p class="clarity-compare-card__sub">Mayo / Cleveland / Penn</p>
            <p class="clarity-body">$4,000–$8,000 for a two-day program. Outstanding diagnostics, followed by a flight home and no ongoing physician relationship. You get a report. We give you a year.</p>
            <p class="clarity-compare-card__quote">"The best single-day assessment money can buy — and then you're on your own."</p>
          </div>
          <div class="clarity-compare-card">
            <h3 class="clarity-h3">vs. Longevity clinics</h3>
